{"tid":2184023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄧冰強: 好多人話因為8.31囉，因為新屋嶺囉，咁呢啲係假嘅嘢嚟嫁","createTime":"2020-09-01T09:41:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T04:44:02.000Z","uid":74778,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bac703583d242cfd4eb3119551e20faebf15ba2e","tid":2184023,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:41:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">其他所有野都係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">7.21元朗事件派口罩者疑似中聯辦新界工作部副部長葉虎。(黃色圈者)時間約6.36 pm。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HPt80tp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHPt80tp.png&h=8f40f3d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J8i5ie4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ8i5ie4.png&h=3090a8ff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R5qCTOq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR5qCTOq.png&h=d57b2455&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/B8QRzVbfLCQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FB8QRzVbfLCQ&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=713d5bd0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/B8QRzVbfLCQ</a><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/16CiwPChpr0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F16CiwPChpr0&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=9af9ba5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/16CiwPChpr0</a><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">咁快唔嬲啦 ?<br />\n幫大家重溫下</span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">如果果日 比人打既係你老婆仔女 <br />\n你點呀 ?</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">黑警鄉黑<br />\n不共戴天!</span><br />\n<br />\n反送中》元朗「藤條車」搜出武士刀、公安帽 車主身分疑點重重<br />\n<br />\n2019-07-27<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕香港反送中「光復元朗」遊行今（27）晚傳出元朗西鐵站旁一輛自小客車後座被人發現放有6根「藤條」，引起遊行民眾不滿。隨後又爆出後車廂放有武士刀、鐵管、木棍以及疑似中國公安帽，經查後車主非華人，疑點重重。<br />\n<br />\n綜合港媒報導，香港「光復元朗」遊行晚間有眼尖民眾發現，路邊一台黑色自小客車後座放有至少6根「藤條」，與上週攻擊市民的白衣歹徒武器相同，引起群眾不滿，砸破車窗並留下「踢走黑社會」等標語。<br />\n<br />\n請繼續往下閱讀...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隨後又有憤怒民眾撬開其後車廂，竟發現內藏「武士刀」、「鐵管木棍」、以及疑似「中國公安帽」，消息傳出香港社群一片嘩然。<br />\n<br />\n《香港01》指出，經查詢車牌後，車主全名為「Karunanayaka Mudiyanselage, Eranda M」，非華人但持有當地身分證，1999年2月3日首次註冊，地址為元朗八鄉錦莆路吳家村。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，現場民眾根據車中電費帳單，指出實際用車者可能為一位住在南邊圍村的「YIP FOO」（粵語音），更有網友懷疑這就是香港中聯辦新界工作部副部長「葉虎」。<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B1CG8yt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB1CG8yt.jpg&h=9836f26a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TLZ2Pcc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTLZ2Pcc.jpg&h=68fa04cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X6VUFiS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX6VUFiS.jpg&h=84126936&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HGovdDT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHGovdDT.jpg&h=21efaa18&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ucSG4Lz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FucSG4Lz.jpg&h=58f304f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f5sjRqz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff5sjRqz.jpg&h=bdf1bf78&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5FC70iV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5FC70iV.jpg&h=2a75a46e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mwHWTDW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmwHWTDW.jpg&h=a296b639&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZTVERqC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZTVERqC.jpg&h=e0c3f695&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BDk5MYX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBDk5MYX.jpg&h=bbd6c0af&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sRc0ASi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsRc0ASi.jpg&h=28c3ff25&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J4s4h5P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ4s4h5P.jpg&h=3927474e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ePHzFja.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FePHzFja.jpg&h=3800756c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qD0UFjb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqD0UFjb.png&h=f79089b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b24b90f860ed3fd0230a8f12062132568fd90c41","tid":2184023,"uid":168138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:43:25.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">曱甴王鄧冰強</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"cb39712664c23ec422134eb1184c118cc2430e5d","tid":2184023,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:58:55.000Z","msg":"新"},{"pid":"95db3afbf2a8fc35aefca005c3344f32dc94e791","tid":2184023,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T04:20:28.000Z","msg":"在"},{"pid":"35e174dad0bb6e56680104b68e1cb6440338d154","tid":2184023,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T04:44:02.000Z","msg":"。一"}]}